Pangolin - a simple sniffer for GNU/Linux
==========================================

This is Pangolin 1.1.


What is it?
-----------

Pangolin is a simple sniffer for GNU/Linux. It was written for
didactical purposes infacts it use raw sockets and some BPF filters.


Build instructions
------------------

$ autoreconf -i
$ ./configure
$ make


